---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Counseling Services in North Idaho | MWRS"
  description="Individual, couples, and family counseling in Coeur d’Alene, Ponderay, Priest River, and Oldtown, with telehealth available anywhere in Idaho."
>
  <main class="subpage">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="subpage-hero">
      <div class="subpage-hero-inner">
        <h1>Counseling Services</h1>
        <p>
          Counseling at Mental Wellness &amp; Relationship Services (MWRS) is
          calm, steady, and human-sized. We work with adults, teens, couples,
          and families across North Idaho to sort through what’s happening,
          make sense of patterns, and move toward practical next steps.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="subpage-btn">
          Start counseling
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Light SEO body -->
    <section class="subpage-section">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Counseling that meets you where you are</h2>
        <p>
          People come to counseling for many reasons: a specific event, a long
          stretch of feeling low or on edge, a relationship that feels stuck, or
          a general sense that something has to change. Sessions are
          collaborative and conversational—you set the pace, and your counselor
          helps you notice patterns and explore what might actually help.
        </p>

        <p>
          We offer individual, couples, and family counseling, with options for
          in-person visits in Coeur d’Alene, Ponderay, Priest River, and
          Oldtown, as well as telehealth for Idaho residents.
        </p>

        <h3>Common reasons people work with us</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Anxiety, panic, or constant “what if” thinking</li>
          <li>Depression, low motivation, or emotional numbness</li>
          <li>Relationship or marriage strain</li>
          <li>Parenting stress and family conflict</li>
          <li>Trauma, grief, or difficult life transitions</li>
          <li>Burnout, overwhelm, or feeling “stuck”</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          You don’t need perfect words or a polished story before you reach out.
          A simple “here’s what’s been going on” is enough to get started.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <section class="subpage-section subpage-cta">
      <div class="subpage-inner">
        <h2>Ready to take the next step?</h2>
        <p>
          Share a bit about what you’re looking for, and our team will help you
          get matched with a counselor and location that fit your situation.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact-us" class="subpage-btn">
          Start counseling
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .subpage {
      background: #f9fafb;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .subpage-hero {
      padding: 10rem 1.5rem 3rem;
      background: #fbfbf9;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }

    .subpage-hero-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .subpage-hero h1 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-hero p {
      margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    /* Outline button (same top & bottom) */
    .subpage-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #0f172a;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0f172a;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      transition:
        background 0.15s ease,
        color 0.15s ease,
        box-shadow 0.15s ease,
        transform 0.15s ease;
    }

    .subpage-btn:hover {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #ffffff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
    }

    /* Body sections */
    .subpage-section {
      padding: 3.0rem 1.5rem 3.2rem;
      background: #e5e9f3;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
    }

    .subpage-cta {
      background: #fbfbf9;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }

    .subpage-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .subpage-section h2 {
      font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-section h3 {
      margin: 1.1rem 0 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .subpage-section p {
      margin: 0 0 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section ul {
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .subpage-section li + li {
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    .subpage-cta p {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
    
  </style>
</Layout>